    "title": "Senior Revenue Manager at Oberoi Hotels",
    "description": "Grow your career with Oberoi Hotels! We are hiring a Revenue Manager for our Nashik team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Oberoi Hotels:\nOberoi Hotels is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Oberoi Hotels!",
